---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Projects | Tory Nguyen">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-8 sm:py-12 md:py-16 theme-transition-all">
    <!-- Header -->
    <div class="mb-12 sm:mb-16">
      <h1 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-4 sm:mb-6 theme-transition-color">
        Projects
      </h1>
      <p class="text-lg text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 leading-relaxed theme-transition-color max-w-2xl">
        A selection of projects I've worked on, from internships to coursework to personal exploration.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Projects Grid -->
    <div class="space-y-8 sm:space-y-12">
      <!-- Martin Brower Project -->
      <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-800/30 hover:border-zinc-300 dark:hover:border-zinc-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl theme-transition-all">
        <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-2 theme-transition-color">
                Martin Brower Supply Chain Internship
              </h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 theme-transition-color">
                Supply Chain Intern • Stockton, CA
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed theme-transition-color">
            During my internship at Martin Brower, I worked on several projects focused on improving supply chain operations and automating manual processes.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mr-3 mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 flex-1 theme-transition-color">
                Worked with warehouse, transportation, and operations teams to identify process improvement opportunities
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mr-3 mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 flex-1 theme-transition-color">
                Migrated a legacy Microsoft Access database to Power Apps and Dataverse, improving data accessibility and management
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mr-3 mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 flex-1 theme-transition-color">
                Automated reporting workflows using Power Automate, significantly reducing manual work and improving efficiency
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mr-3 mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 flex-1 theme-transition-color">
                [[ADD MORE IMPACT BULLETS]]
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-700 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 theme-transition-all">
              Power Apps
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-700 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 theme-transition-all">
              Power Automate
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-700 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 theme-transition-all">
              Dataverse
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-700 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 theme-transition-all">
              Supply Chain
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- NASA L'SPACE Project -->
      <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-800/30 hover:border-zinc-300 dark:hover:border-zinc-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl theme-transition-all">
        <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-2 theme-transition-color">
                NASA L'SPACE Program
              </h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 theme-transition-color">
                Team-based NASA Academy Participant
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed theme-transition-color">
            Participated in the NASA L'SPACE program, a team-based NASA academy focused on systems thinking, project management, and outreach.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-3">
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mr-3 mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 flex-1 theme-transition-color">
                Worked in a team environment on NASA-related projects, applying systems thinking principles
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mr-3 mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 flex-1 theme-transition-color">
                Participated in outreach activities and educational initiatives
              </p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex items-start">
              <span class="text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mr-3 mt-1">•</span>
              <p class="text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 flex-1 theme-transition-color">
                [[ADD MORE DETAILS ABOUT SPECIFIC PROJECTS AND CONTRIBUTIONS]]
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-700 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 theme-transition-all">
              Systems Thinking
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-700 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 theme-transition-all">
              Team Collaboration
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-700 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 theme-transition-all">
              Outreach
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>

      <!-- Course and Personal Projects -->
      <article class="group relative overflow-hidden rounded-2xl border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-800/30 hover:border-zinc-300 dark:hover:border-zinc-700 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl theme-transition-all">
        <div class="p-6 sm:p-8 md:p-10">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-4">
            <div>
              <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-2 theme-transition-color">
                Course & Personal Projects
              </h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400 theme-transition-color">
                Academic and Personal Exploration
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 mb-6 leading-relaxed theme-transition-color">
            Various projects exploring operations research, statistics, engineering labs, and web development.
          </p>
          
          <div class="space-y-4">
            <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800/50 theme-transition-all">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-2 theme-transition-color">
                [[ADD PROJECT TITLE]]
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 theme-transition-color">
                [[ADD PROJECT DESCRIPTION]]
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="p-4 rounded-lg border border-zinc-200 dark:border-zinc-800 bg-white dark:bg-zinc-800/50 theme-transition-all">
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-2 theme-transition-color">
                [[ADD PROJECT TITLE]]
              </h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-400 theme-transition-color">
                [[ADD PROJECT DESCRIPTION]]
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-2">
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-700 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 theme-transition-all">
              Operations Research
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-700 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 theme-transition-all">
              Statistics
            </span>
            <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-700 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-medium text-zinc-800 dark:text-zinc-200 theme-transition-all">
              Web Development
            </span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

